summary: Completed comprehensive testing of TapCard digital business card SaaS platform. All core functionality working correctly including landing page, registration/login, dashboard, profile editing, QR code generation, public profiles, and contact forms.

design_issues.issue: Clipboard write permission denied error in browser console
design_issues.impact: Copy-to-clipboard functionality may not work in some browsers

design_issues.issue: Webpack dev server overlay intercepting pointer events

passed_tests: Landing page loads with hero, features, pricing sections
Registration page loads and form works correctly
Login page loads and form elements present
Backend API /api/ returns correct response
Backend API /api/auth/register creates user and returns data
Backend API /api/auth/login authenticates user
Backend API /api/profile gets and updates user profile
Backend API /api/links manages social links (create, get, delete)
Backend API /api/public/{username} serves public profiles
Backend API /api/public/{username}/contact processes contact forms
Backend API /api/analytics returns user analytics
Dashboard loads for authenticated user with all navigation tabs
Profile editor loads, saves data, and shows live preview
QR code generator works with customization options
Public profile page /u/{username} loads correctly with full functionality
Contact form on public profile works and submits successfully
Links can be added and deleted in dashboard
Save contact (vCard download) functionality works
Share functionality works
Mobile responsive design works correctly

success_percentage.frontend: 95% (all core functionality working, minor browser permission issues)
